on.<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo3;tab-stops:list 45.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:arial;color:#92d050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:=\"\" bold\"=\"\">j.<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#92d050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:=\"\" bold\"=\"\">Address Bar - The Address bar shows the URL (Universal Resource\r\nLocation), also called the <a href=\"\"><span style=\"color:#92D050;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">address</span></a>,\r\nfor the web page that is showing in the browser\'s window. The Links bar is\r\nusually shown to the right of the Address bar. <o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo3;tab-stops:list 45.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:arial;color:#92d050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:=\"\" bold\"=\"\">k.<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#92d050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:=\"\" bold\"=\"\">Status Bar - The Status Bar talks back to you. On its left side you will\r\nsee messages about what browser is doing. The most common message is\r\n\"Done\" <!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\r\n id=\"Picture_x0020_2\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"Description: Statusbar = Done\"\r\n style=\'width:52.5pt;height:18pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square\'>\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\WIN7US~1\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image004.png\"\r\n  o:title=\"Statusbar = Done\"></v:imagedata>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img border=\"0\" width=\"70\" height=\"24\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\WIN7US~1\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtmlclip1\\01\\clip_image004.png\" alt=\"Description: Statusbar = Done\" v:shapes=\"Picture_x0020_2\"><!--[endif]-->,\r\nwhich means that the browser thinks it has finished downloading a web page. <o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:150%;mso-list:\r\nl0 level2 lfo3;tab-stops:list 45.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:arial;color:#92d050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:=\"\" bold\"=\"\">l.<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#92d050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:=\"\" bold\"=\"\">Links Bar - The Links bar is a convenient spot for shortcuts to your most\r\nfrequently accessed web pages. <o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:9.35pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-9.35pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-9.35pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;\r\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:arial;color:#92d050\"=\"\">III.<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#92d050\"=\"\">Searching the web<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:9.35pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-9.35pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-9.35pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;\r\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:arial;color:#92d050\"=\"\">IV.<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span class=\"cap\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#92d050\"=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#92d050\"=\"\">f you are looking for specific information,\r\nrather than just something interesting, you need special help. A <span class=\"term\">search engine</span> or a <span class=\"term\">web directory</span>\r\ncan help you find what you need in the vast pile of web pages around the world.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 45.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:arial;color:#92d050\"=\"\">a.<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#92d050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"=\"\">Search engine<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#92D050\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A\r\n<span class=\"term\">search engine</span> is like an index in the back of a book. A\r\nsearch engine uses a computer program, called an intelligent agent, a <span class=\"term\">spider</span>, a <span class=\"term\">crawler,</span> a <span class=\"term\">robot,</span> or just a <span class=\"term\">bot</span>, which crawls\r\nthrough the Web looking at the pages. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nmargin-left:.25in;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#92d050\"=\"\">Major search engines include:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-.25in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#92D050\"><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#92d050\"=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.yahoo.com/\"><span style=\"color:#92D050\">www.yahoo.com</span></a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-.25in;line-height:150%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol;color:#92D050\"><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#92d050\"=\"\">www.<a href=\"http://www.google.com\"><span style=\"color:#92D050\">Google</span></a>.com<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-.25in;line-height:150%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol;color:#92D050\"><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#92d050\"=\"\">www.<a href=\"http://www.alltheweb.com\"><span style=\"color:#92D050\">AllTheWeb</span></a>.com<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-.25in;line-height:150%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol;color:#92D050\"><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#92d050\"=\"\">www. <a href=\"http://search.msn.com\"><span style=\"color:#92D050\">MSN\r\nSearch</span></a>.com<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-.25in;line-height:150%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol;color:#92D050\"><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#92d050\"=\"\">www.<a href=\"http://www.altavista.com\"><span style=\"color:#92D050\">AltaVista</span></a>.com<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\