span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#92d050\"=\"\">try:&nbsp; \"19th century chairs\" &nbsp;&nbsp;instead\r\nof&nbsp;&nbsp;\"old furniture\" <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nmargin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-list:l3 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#92D050\"><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#92d050\"=\"\">use:&nbsp;\"digital camera reviews\" &nbsp;&nbsp;instead\r\nof&nbsp;&nbsp;\"electronics\" <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#92D050\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Make\r\nsure to watch for words with more than one meaning. If you\'re looking for\r\ninformation on modeling, make sure you specify \"fashion\" or\r\n\"clay.\" <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:150%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo4;\r\ntab-stops:list 45.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#92D050\">c.<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#92D050;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Including and Excluding Words<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#92D050\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; By default, 